Source: llgal
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Brice Goglin <Brice.Goglin@ens-lyon.org>

Package: llgal
Architecture: all
Depends: imagemagick, exiftags, ${perl:Depends}, libimage-size-perl
Provides: llgal
Replaces: igal igal-text
Description: Loulous gallery
  llgal is a on-line gallery generator.
 It is based on igal (most of the interface is the same).
 llgal adds supports for different types of slides including text,
 link and movies, addition of headers and footers in generated HTML
 files, and a few other options.
 Caption may be automatically generated from JPEG EXIF tags.
